snippet.title: Newer Super Mario Bros. Wii Deluxe - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In celebration of the fifth anniversary of the release of Newer Super Mario Bros. Wii, we'd like to announce that an upgraded version is in the works!

The project will feature updated graphics, new music, polished-up level design... and perhaps a little more, too!

Stay tuned for further announcements. Release date is TBD.

Newer DX website: http://newerteam.com/wiidx
